title.rendered: SUPREMA BIOSTATION A2 FINGERPRINT IP ACCESS TERMINAL

content.rendered:
Suprema BioStation A2 is the most advanced fingerprint access control and time attendance terminal featuring Suprema’s next generation biometric technology and security platform.

Features

  • Biometric Fingerprint / Live Finger Detection Supported
  • RF Options : BSA2-OIPW :RFID(13.56MHz MIFARE, DESFire/EV1, FeliCa, iCLASSSE/SR, NFC, ISO14443A)
  • CPU 1.0GHz Quad Core / Memory 1GB RAM + 8GB Flash / LCD 5.0″ IPS LCD Touch / LED Indicator Multi-Color
  • WiFi 802.11 b/g / TCP/IP / RS-485 1ch Host or 1ch Slave (Selectable) / Wiegand 1ch In, 1ch Out
